item.dc:creator: @malimt malimt
item.description:
@malimt wrote:

[quote=“GodexCAB, post:2, topic:515496”]Do you mean giving people rights? such as mod/admin/owner?
if so, Go into characters, select the character, .
It will say rights = o
change it if you want.
0 = player
1 = mod
2 = admin
3 = owner
Those are usually how it works. Sometimes servers have higher rights, for coder, co-owner, donators, etc.[/quote]
no i mean the staff list how it says spots are open or it says the owners names, admins names, mods names, etc… we have mods so i would like to put their name in the staff list
